<div align="center"><span class="textbold_orange">NF&kappa;B Phosphorylation Status Screening Service (Code: pNFKB Service)</span><br /><br /></div>

<span class="textbold_orange">Summary</span><br />
Using our <a href="/NFKB-Phosphorylation-Assay-Kit" target="_blank">EnzyFluo&trade; NF&kappa;B Phosphorylation Assay Kit</a>, we screen for modulators that increase or decrease NF&kappa;B phosphorylation status in cells. We measure the NF&kappa;B phosphorylation kinetics, EC50, and IC50 of cells treated with modulators. Testing can be run on a wide variety of cell lines.
<br />
<br />
